definition: not yet/did not/have not/not/8th earthly branch: 1-3 p.m., 6th solar month (7th July-6th August), year of the Sheep/ancient Chinese compass point: 210°
to set/to fix/to determine/to decide/to order

sentences.english: The optimal postoperative treatment for patients with resectable pancreatic cancer has not yet been determined.
sentences.chinese: 接受切除胰臟癌患者最佳的術後治療，目前仍未確定。
他們還未確定自己準備好了。

sentences.english: North Korea’s military abilities remain uncertain and its aggressive intentions remain unpredictable.
sentences.chinese: 朝鮮的軍事力量仍未確定，侵略意圖也不可預測。

sentences.english: The source of infection for the two brothers remains undetermined and investigations are ongoing.
sentences.chinese: 這兄弟倆的感染源仍未確定，調查正在進行之中。

sentences.english: You know what? I’m moving this one to UNDETERMINED.
sentences.chinese: 哈，我就把這點定義爲未確定的事。

sentences.english: The cause of his illness and death remain undetermined.
sentences.chinese: 他的疾病和死亡原因仍未確定。

sentences.english: The mysterious source of the lake is believed to be an underground river that has yet to be located.
sentences.chinese: 據說，湖水的神祕源頭是還未確定明確方位的地下河。

sentences.english: The final size of the battery has not yet been determined.
sentences.chinese: 電池的最終尺寸則仍未確定。
